Yandex Disk.name: P10a.01
Yandex Disk.description: Does the company clearly disclose its process for responding to non-judicial government demands?

Yandex Disk.name: P10a.02
Yandex Disk.description: Does the company clearly disclose its process for responding to court orders?

Yandex Disk.name: P10a.03
Yandex Disk.description: Does the company clearly disclose its process for responding to government demands from foreign jurisdictions?

Yandex Disk.name: P10a.04
Yandex Disk.description: Do the company’s explanations clearly disclose the legal basis under which it may comply with government demands?

Yandex Disk.name: P10a.05
Yandex Disk.description: Does the company clearly disclose that it carries out due diligence on government demands before deciding how to respond?

Yandex Disk.name: P10a.06
Yandex Disk.description: Does the company commit to push back on inappropriate or overbroad government demands?

Yandex Disk.name: P10a.07
Yandex Disk.description: Does the company provide clear guidance or examples of implementation of its process for government demands?
